" Straighten notes - refreshes syntax, so gets weird if defined in syntax file
" TODO: Why does it mess up syntax?
function! Straighten()
  bufdo 1
  source $VIMRUNTIME/syntax/syntax.vim
endfunction
nnoremap <silent> <Leader>N mM:silent call Straighten()<CR>`M

